-- Patricia Hurtado
-- 2010-06-21T20:50:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/times-square-suspect-shahzad-pleads-guilty-to-attempted-mass-destruction.html

          
          
             Times Square bombing suspect Faisal
Shahzad said he will plead guilty to charges in Manhattan
federal court.  
